org.unisens
Interface AnnotationEntry

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, Entry, TimedEntry
All Known Subinterfaces:
EventEntry
public interface AnnotationEntry
extends TimedEntry

AnnotationEntry is the superclass of EventEntry and SignalEntry and defines the common methods. Direct instances of AnnotationEntry are normally not used.

Author:
Malte Kirst, Joerg Ottenbacher, Radi Nedkov
